The {0}th level: A boxing technique commonly used by street thugs, the punches are chaotic but effective.
column3: วิชาหมัดที่นักเลงในตลาดใช้กันทั่วไป ออกหมัดสับสนไร้แบบแผนแต่กลับใช้ประโยชน์ได้จริง

The {0}th level: The moves are as graceful as flowing clouds and water, dancing with the fan, dazzling.
column3: กระบวนท่าอ่อนช้อยดุจเมฆเคลื่อนวารีคล้อย อาศัยพัดร่ายระบำ งดงามกระจ่างตา

The {0}th level: The brush moves like a dancing dragon and snake, catching the enemy off guard.
column3: ลายพู่กันเฉกมังกรอสรพิษร่ายรำ ทำให้ศัตรูไม่ทันรับมือ

The {0}th level: Aspiring to sail a flat boat on the five lakes, abandoning fame and fortune as if discarding chaff, carrying the wind and moon to play with the clouds and water, treating worldly affairs as if they were floating dust.
Use MP to attack enemies with sound waves, achieving a deafening effect.
column3: อาศัยกำลังภายในแปลงคลื่นเสียงทำร้ายศัตรู สามารถบังเกิดผลเป็นเสียงสะเทือนเลื่อนลั่น

The {0}th level: The tune is solemn and tragic, making the listener clench their fists and shed tears.
A sword technique that complements ground rolling movements, emphasizing the combination of upper and lower, and the integration of form and spirit.
Moving like a dragon emerging from the water, still as a spiritual cat catching a mouse.
Once the unique martial arts of a certain Jianghu sect, the punches are free and easy, delicate and agile.
column3: ครั้งหนึ่งเคยเป็นวิชาเฉพาะของสำนักหนึ่งในยุทธภพ ออกหมัดอิสระไร้ห่วงพะวง งดงามคล่องแคล่ว

The {0}th level: A stick technique created by the founding emperor of Zhao, now common among ordinary people.
column3: วิชาพลองที่คิดค้นขึ้นโดยปฐมกษัตริย์รัฐจ้าว เวลานี้แพร่หลายไปในประชาชนทั่วไป

The {0}th level: Stab with a dagger like a thunderstorm, catching the enemy off guard.
Combining the essence of six spear techniques into one, the movements are simple and fast, and the spear techniques are rich and changeable in an instant.
Extremely fierce, each palm strike has the power to split mountains and rocks.
Like a greedy wolf descending to the world, devouring all obstacles.
The sword is swift, as fast as thunder.
With the momentum of Mountain Breaker, shock the world.
There are seven moves, each one directly attacking the enemy's vital points, each move is critical.
A guqin tune passed down from ancient times, between the strings there are towering mountains and trickling streams.
Strike the enemy off guard with the posture of a silver snake coming out of its hole.

Deal damage to enemies within a fan-shaped range (5-grid radius) in front of you;\nIf not breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Bleeding on the enemy;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflict 20 points of Bleeding.

Deal damage to enemies within a 3-grid radius of yourself and knock them back 2 grids;\nIf not breaking defense: 35% chance to trigger Stagger, Disassembly, Slowed, Broken bone on the enemy;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 15% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and trigger Stagger, Disassembly, Slowed, Broken bone on the enemy;

Deal damage to enemies within a fan-shaped range (5-grid radius) in front of you;\nIf not breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, 50% chance to trigger Vulnerable effect.

Deal damage to enemies within a fan-shaped range (4-grid radius) in front of you;\nIf not breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Blinded on the enemy;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 5% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflict 20 points of Blinded.

Deal damage to enemies within a 5-grid radius and 1-grid radius around yourself;\nIf not breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Bleeding on the enemy;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflict 20 points of Bleeding.
Summon 3 constables to assist in battle within a 3x5 area in front of you.
Summon 5 soldiers to assist in battle within a 4x5 area in front of you, upgraded to 5 generals assisting in battle when your own Level reaches 60.

Deal damage to enemies within a 6x3 range in front of you and knock them back 1 grid;\nIf not breaking defense: additionally reduce the enemy's Qi by 125 points;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 15% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and reduce the enemy's Qi by 250 points.
Increase the Action Speed of friendly characters within a 3-grid radius of yourself by 50%, which expires after 2 actions.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 3 squares around oneself and knocks them back 1 square;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflicts 20 points of Internal Injury on the enemy;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 15% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflicts 40 points of Internal Injury, increases own Critical by 15% (lasts for 2 actions).

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 4 squares around oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 20% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, for every 3 points higher own Sword is than the enemy's Sword, inflicts 1 point of Bleeding on them.
Recovers 25% of lost HP for allies within a radius of 2 squares around oneself.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a fan-shaped range (radius of 5 squares) in front of oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: 35% chance to trigger Confuse effect on the enemy;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 15% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and triggers Confuse effect; when Propriety is above 50, for every point above, reduces enemy's energy by 5 points.
Allies within a radius of 3 squares around oneself gain 1 instance of No damage when hit effect.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 3 squares around oneself and knocks them back 3 squares;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and prevents them from moving in their next action.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 3 squares around oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: 35% chance to trigger Charm effect on the enemy (lasts for 2 actions);\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 20% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, 75% chance to trigger Charm effect on the enemy (lasts for 2 actions).

Inflicts damage on enemies within a 5x1 range in front of oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 5% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, for every 10 points higher own Throwing is than the enemy's Throwing, inflicts 1 point of Bleeding on them.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a fan-shaped range (radius of 4 squares) in front of oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, for every 7 points higher own Throwing is than the enemy's Throwing, inflicts 1 point of Bleeding on them.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 4 squares around oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 15% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, for every 5 points higher own Throwing is than the enemy's Throwing, inflicts 1 point of Bleeding on them.

Deal damage to enemies within a fan-shaped range (4-grid radius) in front of you;\nIf not breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Blinded on the enemy;\n   If breaking defense: additionally inflict 5% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflict 20 points of Blinded.

Inflicts damage on enemies within a radius of 4 squares around oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: 25% chance to trigger Vulnerable effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action);\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, 50% chance to trigger Vulnerable effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action).

Inflicts damage on enemies within a range of 1 square in front of oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 5% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, 50% chance to trigger Charm effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action).

Inflicts damage on enemies within a fan-shaped range (radius of 4 squares) in front of oneself;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflicts 10 points of Poisoned on the enemy;\n   Breaking defense: additionally inflicts 10% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and inflicts 20 points of Poisoned, reduces enemy's current MP by 10%.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 4-tile radius of yourself;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally reduce enemy Action Speed by 10%, Critical, Parry, Evasion by 5% (lasts for 2 actions);\n   With breaking defense: additionally reduce enemy Action Speed by 20%, Critical, Parry, Evasion by 10% (lasts for 2 actions).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 3-tile horizontal range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Blinded on the enemy;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, and inflict 20 points of Blinded.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5x1 range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, for every 7 points your Throwing is higher than the enemy's, inflict 1 point of Internal Injury.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 1-tile range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: 25% chance to trigger Unconscious effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action);\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, 50% chance to trigger Unconscious effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5x1 range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Bleeding on the enemy;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, and inflict 20 points of Bleeding.
Summon 1 hound within a 3x3 range in front of you.

Inflict damage on enemies within a fan-shaped range (4-tile radius) in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Internal Injury on the enemy;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, and inflict 20 points of Internal Injury.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 3-tile radius of yourself and knock them back 1 tile;\nWithout breaking defense: 35% chance to trigger Broken bone effect on the enemy (lasts for 2 actions);\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 15% of the enemy's maximum HP, and trigger Broken bone effect on the enemy (lasts for 2 actions).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 7x3 range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 15% of the enemy's maximum HP, for every 5 points your Long is higher than the enemy's, inflict 1 point of Sealed.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 6x3 range in front of you;\nWithout breaking defense: no additional effects;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 15% of the enemy's maximum HP, for every 5 points your Sword is higher than the enemy's, inflict 1 point of Bleeding.

Inflict the following effects on enemies within a radius of 5 squares of yourself;\nUnbroken Defense: Trigger Stagger, Disassemble, Slowed, Broken Bone on the enemy;\nBroken Defense: For every additional 100MP of your current MP, inflict an additional 1% damage on the enemy, up to 35%; and trigger Stagger, Disassemble, Slowed, Broken Bone on them, after triggering, your MP Cost is emptied, then recover 10% of your maximum MP value with each action (lasts for 3 actions).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 4-tile radius of yourself;\nWithout breaking defense: additionally inflict 10 points of Bleeding on the enemy, and reduce 100 points of their Qi;\n   With breaking defense: additionally inflict damage equal to 10% of the enemy's maximum HP, and inflict 20 points of Bleeding, reduce 175 points of their Qi.
Summon 2 Scorpions to assist in battle within a 3x5 area in front of you.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 4x1 range in front and knock them back 1 square;\nNo defense break: No additional effects;\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 10% of the enemy's max HP as damage.
Summon 4 level 60 generals to assist in battle within a semicircular range of 4 squares in front.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 6x3 range in front;\nNo defense break: 35% chance to trigger either Confuse, Cut tendon, or Vulnerable effect on the enemy;\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 20% of the enemy's max HP as damage, and trigger Confuse, Cut tendon, Vulnerable effects on them; for every 3 points your Sword is higher than the enemy's, inflict 1 point of Bleeding.

Knock back enemies within a 4-square radius of yourself by 3 squares, reduce their Qi by 1000 points, and inflict 25 points of Poisoned, 25 points of Bleeding, 25 points of Internal Injury, 25 points of Sealed, 25 points of Blinded; reduce your own Poisoned, Bleeding, Internal Injury, Sealed, Blinded by 50%, and increase Action Speed by 50% (lasts for 2 actions).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5x5 range in front;\nNo defense break: Inflict an additional 15 points of Internal Injury, 15 points of Sealed, 15 points of Blinded on the enemy;\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 15% of the enemy's max HP as damage, and inflict 30 points of Internal Injury, 30 points of Sealed, 30 points of Blinded on them.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 7x3 range in front;\nNo defense break: 25% chance to trigger Vulnerable effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action);\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 10% of the enemy's max HP as damage, and 50% chance to trigger Vulnerable effect on the enemy (lasts for 1 action).

Inflict damage on enemies within a 2-square radius of yourself;\nNo defense break: Inflict an additional 10 points of Bleeding on the enemy;\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 10% of the enemy's max HP as damage, and inflict 20 points of Bleeding on them.

Inflict damage on enemies within a semicircular range of 5 squares in front;\nNo defense break: Inflict an additional 20 points of Internal Injury on the enemy, and reduce their Qi by 100 points;\n   Defense break: Inflict an additional 15% of the enemy's max HP as damage, inflict 40 points of Internal Injury on them, and reduce their Qi by 175 points.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5x1 range in front;\nWithout breaking defense: No additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: Inflict additional 10% of enemy's max HP as damage.

Recover 10% of lost HP and MP for allies within a 3-square radius around self.
Recover 25% of max HP for self within a 3-square radius.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5-square radius around self;\nWithout breaking defense: 35% chance to trigger Slumber effect on enemy (lasts 2 actions);\n   Breaking defense: Inflict additional 20% of enemy's max HP as damage, 75% chance to trigger Slumber effect on enemy (lasts 2 actions).

Pull a character within a 6-square radius diamond-shaped range around self to the front, if it's an enemy, inflict additional damage, if it's an ally, they get 15% final damage reduction until their next action.\nWithout breaking defense: No additional effects;\n   Breaking defense: Inflict additional 15% of enemy's max HP as damage.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 2-square radius around self and knock them back 1 square;\nWithout breaking defense: Reduce enemy's energy by 100 points;\n   Breaking defense: Inflict additional 15% of enemy's max HP as damage, and reduce enemy's energy by 175 points.

Pull enemies within a radius of 7 squares to yourself and inflict damage, converting 10% of the damage dealt into your own HP.\nUnbroken Defense: No additional effects;\n   Broken Defense: Inflict an additional 20% of the enemy's maximum HP as damage.

Inflict damage on enemies within a radius of 5 squares around yourself;\nUnbroken Defense: No additional effects;\n   Broken Defense: For non-boss enemies lower than your own Level, there is a chance to trigger Instant death, the higher the Level difference, the higher the probability.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5-grid radius of yourself;\nIf the defense is not broken: no additional effects;\nIf the defense is broken: inflict an additional 20% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and the next attack will definitely be critical and combo.

Inflict damage on enemies within a 5-grid radius of yourself;\nIf the defense is not broken: reduce the enemy's Defense by 8% (lasts for 2 actions).\nIf the defense is broken: inflict an additional 20% of the enemy's maximum HP in damage, and reduce the enemy's Defense by 15% (lasts for 3 actions).

Inflict damage on enemies within a semi-circular range of 4 squares in front of you. If any enemy is defeated in this attack, the ultimate move will trigger again if there are still enemies in range.
